It enables organisations to recruit and develop candidates applying for jobs at all levels that require deductive reasoning ability. This form of reasoning is commonly required to support work and decision-making in many different types of jobs and at many levels. Sample tasks for jobs that may require deductive reasoning include, but are not limited to: â€¢ evaluate arguments â€¢ analyse scenarios â€¢ draw logical conclusions
